data.description: Beautiful Barnesville home that is move in ready! This home has a split bedroom plan with the master on the main floor. The home also has a beautiful in ground pool with a nice deck surrounded by a privacy fence. Great schools and close to Gordon College. Don't miss out on this one. Schedule an appointment soon. Preferred lender- Kim Patrick with Nexa Mortgage 678-878-7888 Preferred closing atty- Lueder Larkin and Hunter, Griffin location 470-822-1207 Must use showing time and seller will need 3 hours advance notice due to fur babies.
